text: Yannick Favennec (born 12 August 1958 in Chaudron-en-Mauges, Maine-et-Loire) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Mayenne department, and is a member of the Union of Democrats and Independents. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:People from Maine-et-Loire Category:Independent Republicans politicians Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 15th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Union of Democrats and Independents politicians
